Java Developer Roadmap
│
├── Phase 1: Java Fundamentals
│   ├── Install JDK + IDE
│   ├── Variables, Data Types, Operators
│   ├── Control Flow (if, switch, loops)
│   ├── OOP Basics (Encapsulation, Inheritance, Polymorphism, Abstraction)
│   └── Small Console Projects
│
├── Phase 2: Intermediate Java
│   ├── Strings & StringBuilder
│   ├── Arrays & Collections (ArrayList, HashMap, HashSet)
│   ├── Exception Handling
│   ├── Static, Final, Nested Classes, Enums
│   └── Console Apps (Library, To-Do List)
│
├── Phase 3: Advanced Java
│   ├── File Handling (I/O Streams)
│   ├── Multi-threading & Synchronization
│   ├── Java 8+ Features (Lambdas, Streams, Optional)
│   ├── Generics, Annotations
│   └── Date & Time API
│
├── Phase 4: Databases & JDBC
│   ├── SQL Basics (CRUD, Joins)
│   ├── JDBC (Connection, PreparedStatement, Transactions)
│   ├── DAO Pattern
│   └── CRUD Application
│
├── Phase 5: Frameworks
│   ├── Maven/Gradle
│   ├── Spring Core (DI, Beans)
│   ├── Spring Boot (REST APIs)
│   ├── Spring MVC, Spring Data JPA
│   ├── Hibernate ORM
│   └── Spring Security
│
├── Phase 6: Tools & Deployment
│   ├── Git & GitHub
│   ├── JUnit, Mockito
│   ├── Postman API Testing
│   ├── Logging (SLF4J)
│   └── Docker & CI/CD
│
├── Phase 7: DSA & Interview Prep
│   ├── Data Structures (Stack, Queue, Tree, Graph)
│   ├── Algorithms (Sorting, Searching, DP)
│   ├── Java-specific coding challenges
│
└── Phase 8: Projects
    ├── Library Management System
    ├── Online Banking System
    ├── E-commerce API
    ├── Chat Application
    └── Expense Tracker
